review_blob: This beer is a sweet treat. If you like desserts. Im diabetic. I want to like the flavor she gives me, but its an insulin depleting challenge.

It tastes like a citrusy pillow. The bitter is a nice bitter. Its not too bitter. There isnt an aggressive bitter. A polite bite. I like to buy this beer by the case in the tasting room because its my daily drinker. You have a bad day at work? City Fox. You lose some cash via your shitty investment broker? City Fox. Your mom threw out your 90+ NES games after you moved to college 10 years ago? City Fox. I forgot you, mom! Thanks City Fox.
